    {
      "name": "00 - README",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Overview",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/docs/",
            "description": "**Suggested order (local)**\n1. Run server: `python manage.py runserver`\n2. Register users (pre-verified) → Login (same role) → follow folders\n3. Update collection variables from responses (ids)\n\n**Variables**: base_url, emails/passwords, tokens, *_id fields."
